  "text": "For this reason, as suggested by [CITATION_1] , our main aim is to investigate the use of performance measurement systems within a sample of Italian companies operating in different sectors. In particular, the goal is to analyze the diffusion of advanced management control systems within a sample of FFs and to compare the results achieved with a sample of NFFs.",
